{
  "stem": "9728.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That day we realized, you know, that we should be afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how I felt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you feel?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was nothing to, nothing to be joyful about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, next, next came on December.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On December, we were informed that Lodz will be incorporated into Germany-- that they figured that Lodz-- Lodz is actually in Western, West Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted to take Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, rumors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rumors that they will incorporate-- that they are gonna take over Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Lodz will be under their protection and so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on December, on the last, on the latest, latest part of December-- the last week, or the last two weeks-- one afternoon-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let me come back before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the beginning of December, my parents decided that my brother should go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Warsaw, it was to the east, closer to the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And why did they decide this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they decided that he should go to Warsaw, and in Warsaw, maybe because it's not gonna-- Lodz is not-- Warsaw is not going to be incorporated into Germany, maybe life will be easier there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother decided, and we packed everything, and that he will go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my brother had a, a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, the parent of my brother's girlfriend said, yes, they can go together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother was going together with the girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you have to marry before you go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a different life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't like, like it is now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They give-- will give the blessing that the girl should go with my brother to Warsaw, but they have to marry first.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Manya, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Goldberg.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived also in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went to, to a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
